      "title": "3-hour power cuts from 27th June - 03rd July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) has approved 3 hours power cut from June 27 to July 3.",
        "Accordingly, 1 hour and 40 minutes power shedding will be imposed during daytime and 1 hour and 20 minutes during night for ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW groups.",
        "Two hours power shedding will be imposed for Group CC from 6.00am to 8.00am (except 2nd and 3rd July) while 3 hours power cuts for groups MNOXYZ from 5.00am to 8.00am (except 2nd & 3rd July)"
      ],
